features: 【Open Industrial Vintage Bookcase】: Highly recommend this small bookshelf with a sense of design! Add an artistic touch to your home with the exclusively designed geometric patterned standing shelves. High-quality wood panels paired with thick black metal frames give this bookcase shelf a modern industrial look and a retro design that instantly elevates your home decor.

【Save Space & Great Display】: The dimensions of this vintage bookshelf are 30.79"H*11.81" D*"15.75" W. The corner bookshelf has 3 levels with a 12.87-inch spacing between each level, allowing the shelf to provide generous storage and display space. With its open design and small footprint, our narrow bookshelf is lightweight and delicate, easy to move and organize.

【Multifunctional Small Bookshelf】: The 3-tier bookshelf has a simple design that complements any decor. You can use this freestanding bookcase to store your books, crafts, photo albums, potted plants, etc. Our shelf can be used as a small bookshelf for small spaces, display rack, storage rack, plant shelf, side table, and bedside table, making it the perfect addition to your home office, study room, living room or bedroom.

【Great Value Bookcase】: Freestanding bookcases are made of sturdy metal frames and thick wooden boards, each can hold up to 50 pounds. Its waterproof, wear-resistant coating makes its surface smooth and easy to clean. Our low bookshelf has 4 adjustable legs and locks to the wall, making it less likely to tip over. Coupled with the specially designed metal side bars and the X-shaped bar on the back, the narrow bookcase is more structurally stable and durable.

【Easy Assembly & Customer Service】:Small bookcase comes with clear installation instructions to help you assemble quickly in 20 minutes. If you have any further questions or require assistance with our short bookshelf, please do not hesitate to reach out to us directly. We are dedicated to ensuring your complete satisfaction.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A Bookshelf with Character!
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the Freexployer Small Bookshelf for my home office, and I must say, it's been a great addition to my space. I was in dire need of a bookshelf that could fit into my small office without taking up too much space, and this one fit the bill perfectly.What initially drew me to this bookshelf was its vintage industrial design. I'm a big fan of this style, and I knew it would add a touch of character to my otherwise dull office. And boy, was I right! The bookshelf looks fantastic and gives my office a much-needed personality boost.But the best part about this bookshelf is its functionality. With three tiers, it provides ample storage space for all my favorite reads. I can finally display my books in an organized and visually appealing manner. Plus, the freestanding open shelf concept makes it perfect for showcasing decorative items too. It's not just a bookshelf; it's a statement piece that enhances any room's aesthetics.All in all, I'm extremely happy with my purchase. The Freexployer Small Bookshelf is a true gem for those tight on space but unwilling to compromise on style. If you're looking for a functional and stylish bookshelf that won't take up too much space, I highly recommend giving this one a try. You won't be disappointed!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Small Bookshelf with Vintage Feel
reviews.reviewText: I got this vintage bookshelf in the Retro Brown color, and it not only complements trendy Industrial-style interiors but also goes well with an antique-themed decor. Constructed with MDF Board and black metal, it's remarkably sturdy. While the size is relatively small, I use it as a shelf next to my office desk. It was easy to assemble, and its versatility makes it appealing as a side table, nightstand, or for use in the bathroom. Personally, I usually prefer shelves with a back panel, but the absence of one here makes this small bookshelf convenient for use with electronic devices, like alarm clocks, cell phone chargers, and lamps.
